Asụsụ Anuak ma ọ bụ Asụsụ Anywa bụ asụsụ Luo nke sitere na alaka ọdịda anyanwụ Nilotic nke ezinụlọ asụsụ Nilotic
A na-asụ ya karịsịa n'akụkụ ọdịda anyanwụ nke Etiopia nakwa na mba South Sudan site n'aka ndị Anuak

Aha ndị ọzọ enwekwara ike ikpo asụsụ a gụnyere: Anyuak, Anywa, Yambo, Jambo, Yembo, Bar, Asusu Burjin, Asụsụ Miroy, Moojanga, Asusu Nuro. Anuak, Päri, na Jur-Luwo mejupụtara ụyọkọ asụsụ. Nkọwa zuru oke nke asụsụ Anuak bụ Reh (1996) Anywa Language: Description and Internal Reconstructions, nke gụnyekwara ederede ndị e mebiri emebi.
Asusu Anuak bụkwa ihe a ma ama maka enweghị fricatives phonemic.
